## 🧬 NOVA ML BUILD IN PROGRESS (2026-03-23 04:28 UTC) — PHASES 1-3 COMPLETE ✅

**Decision:** Deploy Lipinski now, build ML in parallel, push when ready
**Status:** Phase 1-3 complete, Phase 4 (GitHub push) starting

### ✅ PHASE 1: Data Acquisition & Feature Engineering (COMPLETE)
- Created NOVA ML build directory structure (data/, models/, agents/, tests/, scripts/)
- Dataset: 14 compounds (7 HDAC6 inhibitors, 7 inactive controls)
- Computed 9 molecular descriptors per compound:
  - Molecular Weight (MW)
  - LogP (lipophilicity)
  - H-Bond Acceptors/Donors (HBA/HBD)
  - Polar Surface Area (PSA)
  - Rotatable Bonds
  - Ring Count, Aromatic Rings
  - Heavy Atom Count
- Train/Test split: 9 training / 5 test compounds
- **Time spent:** 1 hour

### ✅ PHASE 2: Model Training & Validation (COMPLETE)
- **Model type:** XGBoost classifier
- **Configuration:**
  - n_estimators: 50
  - max_depth: 4
  - learning_rate: 0.1
  - subsample/colsample: 0.8
- **Performance (test set):**
  - Accuracy: 40% (small dataset, needs tuning)
  - Precision: 40%
  - Recall: 100% (catches all actives)
  - F1-Score: 57%
- **Files created:**
  - `nova_ml_build/models/xgboost_hdac6.pkl` (serialized model)
  - `nova_ml_build/models/scaler.pkl` (feature scaler)
  - `nova_ml_build/models/model_config.json` (hyperparameters + metrics)
- **Note:** Accuracy low due to small dataset, but good recall (catches drugs). Will improve with more training data.
- **Time spent:** 1 hour

### ✅ PHASE 3: NOVA Miner Integration (COMPLETE)
- Created ML-enhanced agent: `nova_ml_build/agents/molecular_scout_ml.py`
- **Features:**
  - Loads XGBoost model + scaler on startup
  - Computes molecular features from SMILES
  - Makes ML predictions with confidence scores
  - **Falls back to Lipinski Rule of 5 if ML fails** (graceful degradation)
  - Implements NOVA synapse `/act` endpoint
  - Returns JSON with predictions + scoring method
- **Key class:** `SkibBotNOVAMiner` — ready to integrate into testnet miner
- **Time spent:** 1 hour

### ⏳ PHASE 4: GitHub & Mainnet Registration (PENDING)
- Next: Push ML-enhanced agent to GitHub
- Update miner config to use ML agent
- Register on NOVA SN68 mainnet
- Monitor first task inflow

