- **Subnet 36 (Web Agents):** Autonomous agents that automate web tasks (Infinite Web Arena benchmark)
- **Subnet 1 (Apex):** LLM inference & agentic workflows
- **Subnet 19 (DSIS):** Large-scale inference API
- **Astrid Arena:** AI agent finance competitions
- **Masa Arena:** General AI agent competitions

